                    <h3 id="statusResultTitle" class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Thank You!</h3>
                    <p id="statusResultMessage" class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        The information was saved successfully and transferred to customer service for further processing.
                    </p>
